        <div class="terms-section">
            <h2 class="terms-subtitle">We try to support customers to have the best shopping experience at the website with the following purchasing & refund policies:</h2>

            <ol>
                <li>You do not have to receive the goods & pay if the delivered product is not the same as the invoice you ordered, or is damaged during transportation.</li>
                <li>We will not refund if the cake has been delivered to you as requested but you refuse to receive it, or if the damage occurs after the receipt inspection process between you and our delivery staff.</li>
