                <li>In case we have to refund the goods to you and you have made payment via bank transfer before, we must confirm receipt of your successful payment before proceeding with the refund method according to the procedure.</li>
                <li>Any request for immediate refund will not be accepted, we will carry out the payment confirmation check process and transfer the refund within a maximum of 7 working days (maybe sooner).</li>
                <li>Bank transfer will be applied for refund, please provide us with your bank account information when notifying us of your refund request.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
